'''HD曲線'''也稱為'''膠片特性曲線'''、'''感光測定曲線'''或'''密度測定曲線'''，是測量[[攝影|攝影]][[膠卷|膠卷]][[感光性|感光性]]的感光曲線，以19世紀的兩位攝影科學家[[費迪南·赫爾特|費迪南·赫爾特]]與[[維羅·查爾斯·德里菲爾德|維羅·查爾斯·德里菲爾德]]為名。他們將{{tsl|en|Sensitometry|感光測定}}及[[密度測定法|密度測定]]之科學實踐帶入攝影膠卷，並研發一種稱為{{tsl|en|Actinograph|光化儀}}的攝影[[測光表|測光表]]。<ref>{{cite book | title = The Photographic Researches of Ferdinand Hurter & Vero C. Driffield: Being a Reprint of Their Published Papers, Together With a History of Their Early Work & a Bibliography of Later Work on the Same Subject 
 | author = William Bates Ferguson (editor) | publisher = London: Royal Photographic Society of Great Britain | year = 1920 | url = https://archive.org/details/memorialvolumeco00hurtiala}}</ref>

